10:
Please, answer me. I can't take this
anymore—
17: This has nothing to do with me.
23:
If you really want to protect your
sister, don't look away—no matter
how scared you are.
27:
Hide in one of the buildings. Lock the
doors and barricade the windows.
Go!
33: Rgh, come on, let's get this over with!
43:
Now that was a good show... More
for me than for you though.
51:
Wh-what was that?! Where did you
even come from?
54:
From the roofs. Was on my way
back from a delivery when I spotted
you.
56:
Probably not a good idea to wander
out alone right now. Weren't you
with everyone else? And what
happened to your sister?
60:
Arum! Her name is Arum... And she
disappeared on me! I have to find
her!
63:
Can't have a festival without a kid
getting lost...
65: Want me to find her for you?
71:
You could say I've got previous work
experience in this department.
78:
Shush... I'm trying to listen. Your
sister's footsteps are pretty
distinctive.
81:
That way. I think? Maybe? No,
definitely... Probably?
85:
Hm. Is she masking her presence
somehow?
89:
I'm gonna go have a look. Meet up
with you later if I find her.
91:
And hey... Don't push yourself. I think
she'd like to have a sister to come
back to.
96:
As if I'm gonna stay put and do
nothing!
103: That's the last of them over here!
107:
We managed to hold them off for
now.
109:
But Arum is missing. Arly's gone to
look for her.
113:
My apologies. I let her run off on her
own.
116:
...They should be fine. Arum's super
strong, you know?
121: I'm sorry, I've not been much help...
126:
What are you talking about? These
people owe their lives to your first
aid.
129:
Providing assistance is important,
but... My power...
131:
I... I've not been doing all I can to
help!
141: What in the world was that?!
146:
Okay, we just need to hold out long
enough for Stella to get here with
backup.
158:
But in return, I will require yours
afterward!
166:
Whatever it is you need, I hope it's
less dangerous than fighting this
thing!
